This program saved my life. I was fixing a client's computer that had totally crashed. It would not start Windows, safe mode would not work, system restore would not work. I could do nothing to access the files. Thanks to this program I was able to back up the client's files. Safe and easy to use! To clarify, this is basically a compilation of every program offered by Active@
